723133f.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Avenue - 146th Street
723133f.text:
730-28 St. Nicholas Avenue, east side, between 146th and 147th Streets,
showing the unusually large gap between 730 and 732. These houses
were erected in the late 1880's.
About 191O.
